      for guessvalue in range(abs(inp)+1):
          if guessvalue ** 3 >= abs(inp) :
              break
      if guessvalue ** 3 != abs(inp):
          print(str(inp),' is not a perfect cube')
      if inp < 0:
          inp = -inp
      if guessvalue ** 3 ==  abs(inp):
          print('the cube-root of ',str(inp),'is',str(guessvalue))
